    "overview_title": "Amirite?",
    "overview_subtitle": "Determining Slopes of Perpendicular Lines",
    "overview_description": "In this lesson, students explore the relationship between the slopes of perpendicular lines. They use rotations to prove that when two lines are perpendicular, the slopes of the lines are negative reciprocals. Students write the equation of a line perpendicular to a given line that passes through a given point."
  },
